*Prerequisites for Infinite Square Well & Superposition:*
- Energy expectation value: $ chevron.l E chevron.r = sum_n bar.v c_n bar.v^2 E_n $.
- Probabilities: The probability of measuring $E_n$ is $bar.v c_n bar.v^2$.
- Sequential measurements: Measuring an observable collapses the wave function to the corresponding eigenstate. A position measurement collapses the state to a spatial delta function, resetting the energy superposition.
